---
  Choose a default account pool

  Startup found multiple visible account pools and needs a default
  before pooled access can continue.

  Visible pools: team-main, team-other

  Run `mcodex accounts pool default set <POOL_ID>` to choose one of the
  visible pools.

  Press enter or l to log in
